snippet.description:

고립된 사랑(윤아)를 혼자 구하러 간 원(준호). 
킹호텔은 발칵 뒤집히고. 이 일이 약점 잡힐 수도 있지만, 원에게는 상관이 없다. 
추위에 떨면서도 해맑은 사랑을 보며, 원은 사랑의 웃음을 지켜주기로 다짐하는데…
두 사람 앞에 뜻밖의 행운이 찾아온다. 
지리산 일정을 함께 마치고 복귀하는 길, 
원은 사랑을 할머니네에 바래다주다 사랑의 할머니에게 붙잡히게 되는데!

snippet.title: Kim Min Jae and So Ju Yeon Complete Lovestory and Moments in Dr Romantic 3
snippet.description:
Kim Min Jae and So Ju Yeon Complete Lovestory and Moments in Dr. Romantic 3

Viewers' favorite Dimple Couple #kimminjae and #sojuyeon gave viewers something to talk about and look forward to in the recently concluded #drromantic3.

From their break up to their make up, this couple's chemistry could be felt and seen through the screens. 

Most of us were sad when they broke up and were stoked when they shared their make up kiss. #Kimminjae''s confession of love was superb and swoon-worthy. He sees it as uncool, but I thought it was beautiful and sincere.

This video contains #kimminjaeandsojuyeon 's complete moments in #drromanticseason3. I made this edit for those of us who miss seeing them on our screens.

Update: I had to cut out the first segment of the full video due to some YouTube issues. To view the first part of the video, please check out https://youtu.be/jKEaEUnKh4M. Happy viewing!
